snippet.title: Johnny Depp v. Amber Heard: Attorney Andrea Burkhart Analyzes the Latest Court Ruling in Virginia
snippet.description:
Amber Heard / Johnny Depp / Analysis / Court Ruling / 

Criminal defense and appellate attorney Andrea Burkhart discusses the latest ruling in the defamation case Johnny Depp has brought against Amber Heard in Virginia. 

Subscribe to my channel for more on Depp vs. Heard and more interviews with Andrea.
